Apa maksudmu?

00:13:09.560 --> 00:13:10.680
Bahkan hari ini, bibimu

00:13:11.480 --> 00:13:13.720
bisa membaca pikiranmu.

00:13:16.960 --> 00:13:18.760
Kapan Anda akan
mendengarkan hati Anda?

00:13:22.560 --> 00:13:23.720
Ingat satu hal, Virat.

00:13:24.120 --> 00:13:25.920
Antara hati dan otak

00:13:27.560 --> 00:13:28.880
Anda harus selalu
mendengarkan hati Anda.

00:13:32.280 --> 00:13:33.400
Jaga Vinayak.

00:13:36.320 --> 00:13:37.200
Mudah, sayang.

